Package: kraken.com
Title: Kraken Crypto Exchange Market Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Kraken public API. Ticker data,
    OHLC candles, order book depth, recent trades, spread, asset pairs, and
    asset info. No auth for public endpoints.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
